@@TJvCursorImage
Summary
  A TGraphic descendant that can display cursors
Description
  Use TJvCursorImage when you need to display a cursor image on a Canvas.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCursorImage.Assign
Summary
  Copies the content of another object into this object.
Description
  Assign copies the content of another image object into the internal image object. TJvCursorImage
  supports the following Source parameters:
  nil - clear the image
  TJvCursorImage - copies another cursor image into the internal image
  TIcon - copy the image from a TIcon into the internal image
  TBitmap - copy the image from a TBitmap into the internal image
Parameters
  Source - The object to copy from.

